WEBVTT

00:07:29.915 --> 00:07:32.315
and you'll be able to live
very well on that.

00:07:32.339 --> 00:07:36.294
When we talk about jobs going away,
people are alarmed by that,

00:07:36.318 --> 00:07:41.791
because they are dependent on jobs
for their basic material needs of life,

00:07:41.815 --> 00:07:47.886
but the primary concern
will be on meaning and purpose.

00:07:48.276 --> 00:07:52.974
So we have UBI now
in kind of a disorganized way --

00:07:52.998 --> 00:07:57.479
food stamps, housing assistance,
Medicare, Medicaid.

00:07:57.503 --> 00:08:02.840
I befriended a young woman
who was homeless